title: Ep.27: Aaron Rodgers Deal, Lebron James, Steelers QB, Russell Wilson, Mack and Bosa, and Much More!
description: It has been an insane week of sports! This episode was recorded on Sunday so keep that in mind when listening. Lebron James leading the NBA in scoring, packers signing Rodgers and tagging Adams, Wilson and Wentz getting traded, Wagner getting released. The list goes on and on and we have a lot to talk about!
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
